text:
Good work.
Today was pretty rough, huh.

There's that too,
but there's more.

Running around all over the place...
At least properly rest when you're on break.
Why do they have some much energy...?
Maybe it's the change in scenery, or something like that...?

...... I wonder if they realize
that we've got a full schedule tomorrow as well...

If they say something like "I'm too tired～!" then
I won't let them here the end of it...!
Haha... that sounds fair to me...!
Aside from getting dragged around more than usual by those two, no.
...Sorry about that. Thanks for handling it.

── Well, it's fine. Since we're spending more time together, 
something like this was bound to happen.

...But still,
You did say you'd back me up, didn't you?

I know it's pointless to say something like "make those two behave"
but I'm sure you'll do something to heal this exhausted Fuyu, right?
You'll show me how capable you are, right?
